  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK788">
<l>uṭukkai yiḻantavaṉ kaipōla vāṅkē</l>
<l>yiṭukkaṇ kaḷaivatā naṭpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(True) friendship hastens to the rescue of the afflicted (as readily) as the hand of one whose garment is loosened (before an assembly).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
